8. Pricing / Commercial Allocation
Merchandise subtotal là tổng billable paid lines trước invoice-level discounts.
Line gross: originalUnitPrice * quantity.
Line own discount: lineGrossAmount - lineNetBeforeInvoiceDiscount.
Line net before invoice discount: unitPrice * quantity.
Invoice-level manual/promotion/voucher/loyalty discount phải allocate xuống paid merchandise lines.
Allocation weight dùng lineNetBeforeInvoiceDiscount, không dùng quantity, không dùng profit.
lineNetRevenue = lineNetBeforeInvoiceDiscount - allocatedMerchandiseDiscount.
lineCOGS = unitCostSnapshot * quantity.
lineGrossProfitAfterDiscount = lineNetRevenue - lineCOGS.
Reward/free item:
revenue = 0
vẫn trừ stock
vẫn có COGS nếu batch cost > 0
không earn loyalty
Shipping là invoice-level bucket, không phân bổ vào product/category revenue/profit.
VAT truth mới:
vatBase = sum(lineNetRevenue) cho merchandise.
vatAmount = floor(vatBase * vatPercent / 100).
VAT không tính trên shipping.
VAT excluded khỏi revenue/profit.
Product/category reports dùng persisted line net revenue/profit:
revenue = sum(lineNetRevenue)
COGS = sum(lineCOGS)
profit = sum(lineNetRevenue - lineCOGS)
